        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3626834048" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7920103706998574342">Most Americans know Fidel and Che. Some even know Raul. Very few know Camilo, perhaps the most charismatic Cuban rebel of them all. Thorndike does a masterful job of weaving a love story into an alternative history that showcases a fascinating historical figure. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


