    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2535861404" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13963914156861195741">I absolutely loved this book! I received it in a Good Reads giveaway and am glad I did because I would not have ordinarily picked it up to read! The life of old time Cuba and it&apos;s history is so well documented! I love the history of Cuba as told which is interspersed with a love story. The historical facts are so interesting. I learned a lot from the book, from early time Fidel Castro&apos;s reign to present. Very interesting and educational. My copy was also signed by the author on a postcard which </span>
  <span id="freeText13963914156861195741" style="display:none">I absolutely loved this book! I received it in a Good Reads giveaway and am glad I did because I would not have ordinarily picked it up to read! The life of old time Cuba and it's history is so well documented! I love the history of Cuba as told which is interspersed with a love story. The historical facts are so interesting. I learned a lot from the book, from early time Fidel Castro's reign to present. Very interesting and educational. My copy was also signed by the author on a postcard which makes it even more special. Thank you Good Reads for this book!</span>
