<li class='cover' id='bookCover_10836'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/10836.Che_Guevara"><img alt="Che Guevara: A Revolutionary Life" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1406995661l/10836._SX98_.jpg" />
